{"pageid":71278,"pagename":"Merlin's Crystal/Quick guide","title":"Merlin's Crystal/Quick guide","displaytitle":"Merlin's Crystal/Quick guide","revid":14285399,"redirects":["Merlin's crystal/quick guide"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"notoc","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Bring all required items for the quest with you."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Merlin&#39;s Crystal/Quick guide.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Merlin&#39;s Crystal/Quick guide\">rsw:Merlin's Crystal/Quick guide</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"messagebox\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><span class=\"messagebox-title\"><b>This quick guide has an <a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal\" title=\"Merlin&#39;s Crystal\">in-depth guide here</a>.</b></span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\" class=\"messagebox-text\">It contains a more detailed description of dialogue, cutscenes, and storyline.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Talk to <a href=\"/w/King_Arthur\" title=\"King Arthur\">King Arthur</a> in <a href=\"/w/Camelot\" title=\"Camelot\">Camelot</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Intermediate</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">The wizard <a href=\"/w/Merlin\" title=\"Merlin\">Merlin</a> has been trapped in a magical crystal by the witch <a href=\"/w/Morgan_Le_Faye\" title=\"Morgan Le Faye\">Morgan Le Faye</a>. So far, King Arthur hasn't been able to figure out how to free his mentor from his crystal prison. Can you help?</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\nMust be able to defeat a level 39 enemy.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Bread\" title=\"Bread\">Bread</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Tinderbox\" title=\"Tinderbox\">Tinderbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Bucket_of_wax\" title=\"Bucket of wax\">Bucket of wax</a> (obtainable during the quest with <a href=\"/w/Insect_repellent\" title=\"Insect repellent\">Insect repellent</a>, a bucket spawns near the beekeeper)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Bat_bones\" title=\"Bat bones\">Bat bones</a> (obtainable during the quest)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Combat level\" data-level=\"20\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\"><img alt=\"Combat level\" src=\"/images/Attack_style_icon.png?ceb2e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 20 <a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">Combat level</a></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Stamina_potion\" title=\"Stamina potion\">Stamina</a> or <a href=\"/w/Energy_potion\" title=\"Energy potion\">energy potions</a></li>\n<li>Fast travel to several locations\n<ul><li>Camelot (<a href=\"/w/Camelot_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Camelot teleport\">Camelot teleport</a>)</li>\n<li>Falador (<a href=\"/w/Falador_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Falador teleport\">Falador teleport</a>)</li>\n<li>Varrock (<a href=\"/w/Varrock_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varrock teleport\">Varrock teleport</a>, <a href=\"/w/Chronicle\" title=\"Chronicle\">Chronicle</a> or <a href=\"/w/Combat_Bracelet\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Combat Bracelet\">Combat Bracelet</a> to the Champions' Guild)</li>\n<li>Taverley (<a href=\"/w/Taverley_teleport\" title=\"Taverley teleport\">Taverley teleport</a>, <a href=\"/w/Balloon_Transport_System\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Balloon Transport System\">Balloon Transport System</a> or <a href=\"/w/Teleport_to_House\" title=\"Teleport to House\">Teleport to House</a> if your house is in Taverley)</li>\n<li>Port Sarim (<a href=\"/w/Explorer%27s_Ring_2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Explorer&#39;s Ring 2\">Explorer's Ring 2</a>, <a href=\"/w/Rat_Pits\" title=\"Rat Pits\">Rat Pits</a> or <a href=\"/w/Pest_Control\" title=\"Pest Control\">Pest Control</a> <a href=\"/w/Minigame\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Minigame\">minigame</a> teleport, or <a href=\"/w/Teleport_to_House\" title=\"Teleport to House\">Teleport to House</a> if your house is in Rimmington)</li></ul></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Sir_Mordred\" title=\"Sir Mordred\">Sir Mordred</a> <i>(level 39)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Giant_bat\" title=\"Giant bat\">Giant bat</a> <i>(level 27)</i> (optional, to acquire <a href=\"/w/Bat_bones\" title=\"Bat bones\">bat bones</a>)</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;Must be able to defeat a level 39 enemy.&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;The wizard &#91;&#91;Merlin&#93;&#93; has been trapped in a magical crystal by the witch &#91;&#91;Morgan Le Faye&#93;&#93;. So far, King Arthur hasn&#39;t been able to figure out how to free his mentor from his crystal prison. Can you help?&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Intermediate&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;* &#91;&#91;Sir Mordred&#93;&#93; &#39;&#39;(level 39)&#39;&#39;\\n* &#91;&#91;Giant bat&#93;&#93; &#39;&#39;(level 27)&#39;&#39; (optional, to acquire &#91;&#91;bat bones&#93;&#93;)&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;Merlin&#39;s Crystal/Quick guide&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Talk to &#91;&#91;King Arthur&#93;&#93; in &#91;&#91;Camelot&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;*&#91;&#91;Bread&#93;&#93;\\n*&#91;&#91;Tinderbox&#93;&#93;\\n*&#91;&#91;Bucket of wax&#93;&#93; (obtainable during the quest with &#91;&#91;Insect repellent&#93;&#93;, a bucket spawns near the beekeeper)\\n*&#91;&#91;Bat bones&#93;&#93; (obtainable during the quest)&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Getting_started\">Getting started</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Getting started\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Getting started\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<p>Bring all required items for the quest with you.\n</p>\n<ul><li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/King_Arthur\" title=\"King Arthur\">King Arthur</a>. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I want to become a knight of the round table!\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-d3281f768017f3b8f48c412a54211cab\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-d3281f768017f3b8f48c412a54211cab\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>I want to become a knight of the round table!</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Sir_Gawain\" title=\"Sir Gawain\">Sir Gawain</a>, who can be found in the courtyard to the south or nearby in the castle. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Do you know how Merlin got trapped?\">3</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-4d818ed1de83c6eff73c1d4cc5fca2c4\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-4d818ed1de83c6eff73c1d4cc5fca2c4\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>Do you know how Merlin got trapped?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Sir_Lancelot\" title=\"Sir Lancelot\">Sir Lancelot</a> upstairs. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Any ideas on how to get into Morgan Le Faye&#39;s stronghold?\">3</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-848ca044d92f5e14ef131170412d3a8d\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-848ca044d92f5e14ef131170412d3a8d\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>Any ideas on how to get into Morgan Le Faye's stronghold?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Go to <a href=\"/w/Catherby\" title=\"Catherby\">Catherby</a>.\n<ul><li>If you didn't bring a bucket of wax, grab <a href=\"/w/Insect_repellent\" title=\"Insect repellent\">insect repellent</a> in the house north of the bank in Catherby.</li>\n<li>Use the insect repellent on one of the beehives to the west with an empty bucket (a bucket can be found near the beehives) in your inventory to get a bucket of wax.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Hide in the crate north of the <a href=\"/w/Candle_maker\" title=\"Candle maker\">candle maker</a>'s shop. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-cb893ed7bca34c717cb68d84b521fd62\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-cb893ed7bca34c717cb68d84b521fd62\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> Wait and finish the cutscene. Climb out of the crate. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-cb893ed7bca34c717cb68d84b521fd62\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-cb893ed7bca34c717cb68d84b521fd62\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Inside_the_keep\">Inside the keep</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Inside the keep\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Inside the keep\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Climb to the top floor. The <a href=\"/w/Renegade_Knight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Renegade Knight\">Renegade Knights</a> will attack you on your way up.</li>\n<li>Attack <a href=\"/w/Sir_Mordred\" title=\"Sir Mordred\">Sir Mordred</a>. He cannot be safespotted, but he can be flinched using the stairs (position him on the square left of the stairs whilst flinching from the square north-east of him). He can also be killed with <a href=\"/w/Rings_of_recoil\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rings of recoil\">rings of recoils</a> or by another account poisoning and attacking right before his death.</li>\n<li>When Sir Mordred reaches 0 hitpoints, Morgan Le Faye will appear and ask that you spare him. Spare his life to discover how to save Merlin. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Tell me how to untrap Merlin and I might.\">1</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"OK I will do all that.\">2</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-270e36d187936c9491f298c847e747d5\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-270e36d187936c9491f298c847e747d5\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Tell me how to untrap Merlin and I might.</td></tr><tr><td><b>2</b></td><td>OK I will do all that.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> <span style=\"color:red;\">Warning:</span> Do <b>not</b> interrupt the dialogue or you will have to fight Sir Mordred again.\n<ul><li>If you don't already have bat bones, exit the keep through the west doors and kill a bat before leaving.</li>\n<li>Can be recoiled down after dealing a 0 and not splashing Magic.</li></ul></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Black_candle\">Black candle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Black candle\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Black candle\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Talk to the candle-maker in Catherby. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Have you got any black candles?\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-0675c0531b5fac62eaea8599601fb6f6\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-0675c0531b5fac62eaea8599601fb6f6\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Have you got any black candles?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Talk to him again for a black candle.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Excalibur\">Excalibur</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Excalibur\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Excalibur\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/The_Lady_of_the_Lake\" title=\"The Lady of the Lake\">The Lady of the Lake</a> south-east of <a href=\"/w/Taverley\" title=\"Taverley\">Taverley</a> on the peninsula. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I seek the sword Excalibur.\">3</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-f1a712bb19dfc336ce1fedfee4eafc7d\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-f1a712bb19dfc336ce1fedfee4eafc7d\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>I seek the sword Excalibur.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Go to <a href=\"/w/Port_Sarim\" title=\"Port Sarim\">Port Sarim</a>. (Make sure you have bread in your inventory.)</li>\n<li>Enter the ring shop to the north.</li>\n<li>Give the beggar your bread. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes certainly.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-b2cf6a2f9e4895ae5c8076cf22905330\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-b2cf6a2f9e4895ae5c8076cf22905330\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes certainly.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> Finish the conversation.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ritual\">Ritual</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Ritual\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Ritual\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go to the Zamorakian temple in the south-east corner of Varrock.</li>\n<li>Check the Chaos Altar's inscription.</li>\n<li>Return to Camelot with a tinderbox and enter the castle gates.</li>\n<li>Go to the ritual site at the north-east corner of the Camelot castle grounds (a red star in the middle of 8 columns).</li>\n<li>Stand on the star and light the black candle.</li>\n<li><b>Drop</b> the bat bones on the star.</li>\n<li>The magic words are \"Snarthon Candtrick Termanto\".</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Finishing_up\">Finishing up</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Finishing up\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Finishing up\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Enter the castle and climb to the top of the south-east tower.</li>\n<li>Smash the giant crystal with Excalibur. (<b>Does not</b> require 20 Attack, just use Excalibur on the crystal instead of attempting to wield it)</li>\n<li>Talk to King Arthur.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><b>Quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?section=9&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Merlin%27s_Crystal_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Merlin&#39;s Crystal reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Merlin%27s_Crystal_reward_scroll.png?4bc8a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>6 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest points</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Excalibur\" title=\"Excalibur\">Excalibur</a> (Required for <a href=\"/w/Holy_Grail\" title=\"Holy Grail\">Holy Grail</a> quest.)</li>\n<li>Completing this quest awards the player with 5 <a href=\"/w/Kudos\" title=\"Kudos\">Kudos</a> which can be claimed by talking to <a href=\"/w/Historian_Minas\" title=\"Historian Minas\">Historian Minas</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Varrock_Museum\" title=\"Varrock Museum\">Varrock Museum</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Merlin&#39;s Crystal\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Merlin%27s_Crystal\" title=\"Template:Merlin&#39;s Crystal\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Merlin%27s_Crystal\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Merlin%27s_Crystal?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Merlin%27s_Crystal\" title=\"Merlin&#39;s Crystal\">Merlin's Crystal</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title