class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Bucket_of_wax\" title=\"Bucket of wax\"><img alt=\"Bucket of wax.png\" src=\"/images/Bucket_of_wax.png?c50c3\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Bucket_of_wax\" title=\"Bucket of wax\">Bucket of wax</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Insect_repellent\" title=\"Insect repellent\"><img alt=\"Insect repellent.png\" src=\"/images/Insect_repellent.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"18\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Insect_repellent\" title=\"Insect repellent\">Insect repellent</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Candles</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Candle\" title=\"Candle\"><img alt=\"Candle.png\" src=\"/images/Candle.png?39d34\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"8\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"8\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Candle\" title=\"Candle\">Candle</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lit_candle\" title=\"Lit candle\"><img alt=\"Lit candle.png\" src=\"/images/Lit_candle.png?6dc61\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"8\" height=\"32\" data-file-width=\"8\" data-file-height=\"32\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Lit_candle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lit candle\">Lit</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Black_candle\" title=\"Black candle\"><img alt=\"Black candle.png\" src=\"/images/Black_candle.png?356fd\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"8\" height=\"25\" data-file-width=\"8\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Black_candle\" title=\"Black candle\">Black</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lit_black_candle\" title=\"Lit black candle\"><img alt=\"Lit black candle.png\" src=\"/images/Lit_black_candle.png?8cc7e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"8\" height=\"32\" data-file-width=\"8\" data-file-height=\"32\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Lit_black_candle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lit black candle\">Lit black</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Rewards</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Excalibur\" title=\"Excalibur\"><img alt=\"Excalibur.png\" src=\"/images/Excalibur.png?b8cf0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"17\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Excalibur\" title=\"Excalibur\">Excalibur</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Camelot\" title=\"Camelot\">Camelot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Catherby\" title=\"Catherby\">Catherby</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Keep_Le_Faye\" title=\"Keep Le Faye\">Keep Le Faye</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Port_Sarim\" title=\"Port Sarim\">Port Sarim</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Taverley\" title=\"Taverley\">Taverley</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quick Guide</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐qlz7t\nCached time: 20220517153136\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.177 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.230 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 725/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 55697/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 10602/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.024/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1527636/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  164.674      1 -total\n 39.56%   65.145      1 Template:Quest_details_page\n 19.02%   31.319      6 Template:Checklist\n 15.76%   25.958      3 Template:Navbox\n 14.79%   24.360      1 Template:Quest_rewards_page\n 12.51%   20.593      1 Template:Merlin's_Crystal\n 10.47%   17.243      9 Template:Chat_option\n 10.09%   16.619      1 Template:External\n  5.58%    9.190      7 Template:Ctg\n  3.45%    5.688      1 Template:Quick_Guide\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:71278-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517153136 and revision id 14285399. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n{{Quick Guide}}\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details page|Merlin's Crystal}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n===Getting started===\n{{Checklist|Bring all required items for the quest with you.\n*Talk to [[King Arthur]]. {{Chat option|1I want to become a knight of the round table!}}\n*Talk to [[Sir Gawain]], who can be found in the courtyard to the south or nearby in the castle. {{Chat option|3Do you know how Merlin got trapped?}}\n*Talk to [[Sir Lancelot]] upstairs. {{Chat option|3Any ideas on how to get into Morgan Le Faye's stronghold?}}\n*Go to [[Catherby]].\n**If you didn't bring a bucket of wax, grab [[insect repellent]] in the house north of the bank in Catherby.\n**Use the insect repellent on one of the beehives to the west with an empty bucket (a bucket can be found near the beehives) in your inventory to get a bucket of wax.\n*Hide in the crate north of the [[candle maker]]'s shop. {{Chat option|1Yes}} Wait and finish the cutscene. Climb out of the crate. {{Chat option|1Yes}}\n}}\n\n===Inside the keep===\n{{Checklist|\n*Climb to the top floor. The [[Renegade Knight]]s will attack you on your way up.\n*Attack [[Sir Mordred]]. He cannot be safespotted, but he can be flinched using the stairs (position him on the square left of the stairs whilst flinching from the square north-east of him). He can also be killed with [[rings of recoil]]s or by another account poisoning and attacking right before his death.\n*When Sir Mordred reaches 0 hitpoints, Morgan Le Faye will appear and ask that you spare him. Spare his life to discover how to save Merlin. {{Chat option|1Tell me how to untrap Merlin and I might.|2OK I will do all that.}} {{Colour|red|Warning:}} Do '''not''' interrupt the dialogue or you will have to fight Sir Mordred again.\n**If you don't already have bat bones, exit the keep through the west doors and kill a bat before leaving.\n**Can be recoiled down after dealing a 0 and not splashing Magic.}}\n\n===Black candle===\n{{Checklist|\n*Talk to the candle-maker in Catherby. {{Chat option|1Have you got any black candles?}}\n*Talk to him again for a black candle.\n}}\n\n===Excalibur===\n{{Checklist|\n*Talk to [[The Lady of the Lake]] south-east of [[Taverley]] on the peninsula. {{Chat option|3I seek the sword Excalibur.}}\n*Go to [[Port Sarim]]. (Make sure you have bread in your inventory.)\n*Enter the ring shop to the north.\n*Give the beggar your bread. {{Chat option|1Yes certainly.}} Finish the conversation. \n}}\n\n===Ritual===\n{{Checklist|\n*Go to the Zamorakian temple in the south-east corner of Varrock. \n*Check the Chaos Altar's inscription.\n*Return to Camelot with a tinderbox and enter the castle gates.\n*Go to the ritual site at the north-east corner of the Camelot castle grounds (a red star in the middle of 8 columns).\n*Stand on the star and light the black candle.\n*'''Drop''' the bat bones on the star.\n*The magic words are \"Snarthon Candtrick Termanto\".\n}}\n\n===Finishing up===\n{{Checklist|\n*Enter the castle and climb to the top of the south-east tower.\n*Smash the giant crystal with Excalibur. ('''Does not''' require 20 Attack, just use Excalibur on the crystal instead of attempting to wield it)\n*Talk to King Arthur.\n}}\n\n'''Quest complete!'''\n\n==Rewards==\n{{Quest rewards page|Merlin's Crystal}}\n\n{{Merlin's Crystal}}"}